QuestData.Title: Return to Keeshan
QuestData.Description: Well I suppose I'm done with you here. I'll go shoo those other warlocks out when I build up the courage.$b$bHere, don't forget those supplies.
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring the Warlock's Supplies back to John J. Keeshan at Flamestar Post in Burning Steppes.
QuestData.CompletionText: It looks like you managed to deal with Gorzeeki.
QuestData.RewardText: <Keeshan looks through the crate.>$b$bGood, good, good. We can move on. Our war takes us east, away from Blackrock Mountain... for now.
